ObjectStates.Name: Bag
ObjectStates.Description:
This pack contains:
1 Character + Starting Item
6 Loot Cards
6 Treasure
6 Monster
2 Bosses
1 Room
1 Bonus Soul

To use this pack, simply right click and click on "Save Object". Now you can load it onto any table you want. Have Fun :)
